sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard
    participant KServeCtrl as KServe Controller
    participant ODHModelCtrl as odh-model-controller
    participant Gateway as Envoy Gateway
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime (vLLM/TGIS/OVMS)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over User,Client: Workflow 1: Model Serving (KServe InferenceService)

    User->>Dashboard: Login via OIDC (kube-auth-proxy)
    Dashboard-->>User: Show model serving UI

    User->>Dashboard: Create InferenceService CR
    Dashboard->>KServeCtrl: CR created in user namespace

    KServeCtrl->>KServeCtrl: Reconcile: Create Deployment, Service, HTTPRoute
    KServeCtrl->>Gateway: Register HTTPRoute
    ODHModelCtrl->>ODHModelCtrl: Create Route, EnvoyFilter, monitoring resources

    Note over Runtime: Pod starts, pulls image from quay.io
    Runtime->>S3: Download model artifacts (HTTPS/443, AWS IAM)
    Note over Runtime: Model loaded, ready to serve

    Client->>Gateway: POST predict (HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+)
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward via HTTPRoute
    KRBAC->>KRBAC: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview
    KRBAC->>Runtime: Forward to model runtime (HTTP/8000)
    Runtime-->>KRBAC: Inference response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON prediction result (HTTPS)

    User->>Dashboard: View model metrics
    Dashboard->>Dashboard: Query Thanos (Bearer token)
    Dashboard-->>User: Model status + metrics
